data.description: This 3 BR, 3 Bath home on a *TRIPLE LOT* offers gulf access without any bridges, making it an ideal location for those who love to spend time out on the water. Located just 20 minutes from the Gulf, you will have easy access to all the boating and fishing opportunities the area has to offer. The highlight of this home is its beautiful salt water pool, which has just been refinished and is perfect relaxing on a warm summer day. The home has been fully remodeled. Fresh paint throughout. A brand new kitchen has been installed with white cabinets and a pantry cabinet. There are brand new quartz countertops along with stainless steel appliances, creating a beautiful and modern space to prepare meals and entertain guests. All bedrooms are located on the same side of the home resulting in a large space for the open kitchen and living area combination perfect for entertaining family and friends. Luxury vinyl flooring adds to the updated and modern feel of the space, creating a cohesive and stylish interior. The home's roof was installed in 2018. Full house generator with propane tank! *OVERSIZED* 2 car garage! The dock has been refinished and includes 10,000#lift. This location is ideal! It is close to Tarpon Point Marina, offering waterfront shops and restaurants just a short distance away. This home is like new for some lucky new owner to enjoy
